## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="bdd6e-102"><xref:System.Windows.Forms.FlowDirection>枚举描述连续 UI 元素的流动方向，通常为控件，在设计图面或如窗体的容器上。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bdd6e-102">The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.FlowDirection> enumeration describes the flow direction of consecutive UI elements, typically controls, on a design surface or container such as a form.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bdd6e-103">如由线性布局容器使用此枚举<xref:System.Windows.Forms.FlowLayoutPanel>，它用于存储此信息在内部<xref:System.Windows.Forms.FlowLayoutPanel.FlowDirection%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bdd6e-103">This enumeration is used by linear layout containers such as <xref:System.Windows.Forms.FlowLayoutPanel>, which stores this information internally in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.FlowLayoutPanel.FlowDirection%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="bdd6e-104"><xref:System.Windows.Forms.FlowDirection>确定新控件的位置按默认添加到支持容器时。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bdd6e-104">The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.FlowDirection> determines where a new control is placed by default when it is added to a supporting container.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bdd6e-105">流方向的容器，连同<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Anchor%2A>和<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Dock%2A>的每个属性包含控件，确定重新排列控件时调整其容器的大小时。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bdd6e-105">The flow direction of the container, along with the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Anchor%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Dock%2A> properties of each contained control, determine the rearrangement of controls when their container is resized.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="bdd6e-106"><xref:System.Windows.Forms.FlowLayoutPanel>控件提供`FlowBreak`于其子控件的属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bdd6e-106">The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.FlowLayoutPanel> control provides a `FlowBreak` property to its child controls.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bdd6e-107">值设置`FlowBreak`属性`true`导致<xref:System.Windows.Forms.FlowLayoutPanel>控件停止对当前排列方向和换行到下一步的行或列中的控件进行布局。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bdd6e-107">Setting the value of the `FlowBreak` property to `true` causes the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.FlowLayoutPanel> control to stop laying out controls in the current flow direction and wrap to the next row or column.</span></span>  
  
   
  
